headline: Shake Shack (SHAK) Q4 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: Shake Shack (SHAK) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.55% and -0.47%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
